<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@300..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Fredoka", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background: #35424a;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #e8491d;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .about-section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: #D9F2B4;
        }

        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .team-section {
            background-color: #B4EBCA;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .team-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .team-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .team-member img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #212529;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        footer p, footer ul {
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #D3FAC7;
        }

        footer ul {
            padding-left: 0;
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
    </style>
    <title>About Us</title>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our blogging platform! We are a passionate team dedicated to creating a space where you can express your thoughts, share your experiences, and connect with a community of like-minded individuals. Our mission is to inspire and empower you through insightful content, diverse perspectives, and engaging stories.</p>
        <p>Whether you're here to read, write, or both, we're thrilled to have you on board. Start your blog journey with us and make your voice heard.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="team-section">
        <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
        <div class="team-wrapper">
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/75.jpg" alt="Team member 1">
                <h3>John Doe</h3>
                <p>Founder & Chief Editor</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/65.jpg" alt="Team member 2">
                <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                <p>Content Strategist</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Team member 3">
                <h3>Mark Wilson</h3>
                <p>Tech Lead</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Your Blog Name. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            <ul class="list-inline">
                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="/contactus">Contact</a></li>
                
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>
